title: 5 Best Laptops Under ₹50,000 – Don't Make Mistake !
description:
laptop kharid liye jaye doston !

🔥 Subscribe for Tabahi Videos

If you're planning to buy a new laptop in 2025, these top models under ₹60,000–₹80,000 should be on your radar! Starting with the Asus Vivobook 15 featuring the powerful Intel Core i5 12th Gen 12500H processor, it's a perfect choice for students and working professionals who want great daily performance with strong multitasking.

For gamers, the HP Victus powered by AMD Ryzen 5 5600H and NVIDIA RTX 3050 GPU offers excellent value, capable of handling AAA gaming and creative workloads without breaking the bank. Another balanced option is the Acer Aspire 7, which comes with a 6-core Intel i5 12450H processor, RTX 2050 graphics, and a 144Hz IPS display, making it a superb laptop for both gaming and productivity at a budget price.

If you prioritize vibrant visuals and content consumption, the ASUS Vivobook OLED with FHD OLED display and Ryzen 5 7520U offers unmatched color quality for binge-watching, editing photos, and casual tasks, packed in a stylish lightweight body.

For hardcore gamers and performance seekers, the ASUS TUF A15 with Ryzen 5 7535HS and RTX 3050 GPU is built for heavy gaming, video editing, and multitasking with durable TUF military-grade build quality and excellent thermal management.

Special Mentions:
The Honor MagicBook X16 with Intel i5 12450H provides a clean design and solid day-to-day performance for students and office users, while the Lenovo Ideapad Gaming 3 with AMD Ryzen 5 5500H, RTX 2050, and a 144Hz FHD display remains one of the most value-for-money gaming laptops in the midrange category.

Whether you're looking for the best laptop for gaming under ₹70,000, a daily use laptop with OLED display, or a budget RTX laptop for creators, these options offer excellent combinations of performance, display quality, battery life, and future-proof specs.

title: टॉडलर्स और किड्स के लिए बेस्ट टॉय लर्निंग वीडियो सरप्राइज क्रेयॉन के साथ रंग सीखें!
description: टॉडलर्स और किड्स के लिए बेस्ट टॉय लर्निंग वीडियो सरप्राइज क्रेयॉन के साथ रंग सीखें! टॉडलर्स, बच्चों और शिशुओं के लिए इस प्रीस्कूल टॉय लर्निंग वीडियो में, टॉडलर्स को रंग, सामान्य शब्द और सरल वाक्य सिखाएं इस सरप्राइज टॉय एजुकेशनल वीडियो के साथ। हम अपने प्रत्येक इंद्रधनुषी रंग के क्रेयॉन को आश्चर्यजनक खिलौनों और हर एक में रंगीन गमबल्स के लिए खोलेंगे। टॉडलर्स के लिए यह टॉय लर्निंग वीडियो बच्चों को सरल शब्द, अवधारणाएं सिखाने और रंगों को पहचानने का एक शानदार, रंगीन तरीका है!
